  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "The Markdown versus H T M L debate. It is still going.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6679b1fa452413218a7a306cf6800f26d8c96e8d140df3615195cf5e290691be",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "One post. Seven days. And the dev internet went to war.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9381edded443d871deb0ea2f2fbe654f8d3b4e663e4e248804be0f90b938ff05",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 3.4829931972789114,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 12
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Thariq, the engineer from Anthropic, dropped a thesis.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7b081fcb87163a6bbc02453410bb789a464722a41443b4eaddcd3d71244f1947",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 23
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Markdown is the wrong format. Seven hundred fifty thousand views.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d98d770c56965f73b7fd846c61fdc0c8b2d757220f6154d44360f920f05a259b",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 3.9938321995464854,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 31
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "The replies split. The Markdown camp came swinging.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c5200f8c42574024fb5574a6ac99bfcbb6331129893f833c91e589f538063a2d",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 41
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Three hundred and sixty-nine likes. Simplicity is the feature, not a bug.",
      "checksum": "sha256:31befdd93837d173ab3a80f10f01ff4c8205be22e534746d59a37f6f66b05d21",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 4.179591836734694,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 49
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "And the structural one. Markdown was designed to compile to H T M L.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b5b62026ae01f574ba7002fa9ce134688ff553b09d47c955fe116c4cef55f0b6",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 5.061950113378685,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 61
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "They are not opposing formats. Then came the receipts.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cff37b8d3b091190510e52fe4f550bcddaef3c9112952ec191a51de9a2946683",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 75
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Twenty-five thousand tokens to generate one H T M L file.",
      "checksum": "sha256:29fabf4ff2e8ee4aabd0f84d0b006b3da3b651e1591b9033b090f16b43706766",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 3.5294331065759637,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 84
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "One thousand tokens for the same content in markdown.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f33d7cf630b0e17887f1e944137b7988e4a2037c334ac955eb54652799d2602a",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 95
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Twenty-five times more tokens. Per artifact.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fcc1be49fa7c00674765944f7d8aece741fc28fd6cb4f94ea730d91778be84b1",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 2.5541950113378684,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 104
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Then four days ago, Thariq doubled down.",
      "checksum": "sha256:82f84465d26c2c6d0d49b42e27c50bc8dc8bd58ea110bb23ad54ca04aed3944c",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 2.043356009070295,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 110
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "One line. H T M L continues to be undefeated.\n\nBut the consensus is forming.",
      "checksum": "sha256:207b20e665c16575eb234faef8872f524ec5b61f05c8cf57bf0b2f06ba3bd00a",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 4.551111111111111,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 117
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Slowly. Out loud. In public. For agents talking to agents.",
      "checksum": "sha256:624b957a3caf62b75448d6f48986ba54090f8f8dd0f9c22b93c3b2c23b45e92b",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 3.5294331065759637,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 132
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "Specs. Plans. Claude dot M D files. Markdown stays.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4fbd580b28d9f01191d37ae8a87c51d5abbda681979fe19cc7a9a828798239f5",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 142
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "For anything a human actually looks at. Reports.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2d321131ac0cb53ccfaac09af21adba9dbef39e447467751591d3775ad9eacce",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 151
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Reviews. Mockups. H T M L wins. The thesis that holds across both camps.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7af803d482ffccfeb840edf58eea2805de9d54df61089b9ba0c1140bb051f32d",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 5.712108843537415,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 159
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "Wherever a human looks, H T M L. So which side are you on?",
      "checksum": "sha256:729e4733e505869f1a0d8f16a41cef75308f946acddb3296d8968f1681bd2bd7",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 3.622312925170068,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 173
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "Markdown for everything. H T M L for everything.",
      "checksum": "sha256:aebb1949ed5e65ba31f0f348c58c340bdaeeea4b1acb74c0611cdfbccf29e41d",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 187
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "Or the hybrid. Drop your pick below. The full video has all the receipts.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f1e9cb564ff9623219ff12be3204a280beae4685d8ae1044b72b7ac5c0feca3a",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 5.108390022675737,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 196
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "Link in the description. And if you want to learn more about A I, check out the dynamous dot A I community.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8d2775004a2b37d1a4c77bd4909f11743ba7f171d7e86705c7689d6938fbf728",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 6.6873469387755105,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 210
    }
  ]
}